{"type":"message","id":"cf705df0","parentId":"da6e01a2","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:40:08.098Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5454919890a0b37add328568d0d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 09:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5454919890a0b37add328568d0d]\nou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e: 重新安装qq"}],"timestamp":1773538808096}}
{"type":"message","id":"85e7774f","parentId":"cf705df0","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:40:23.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求\"重新安装QQ\"。这是关于重新安装腾讯QQ软件的请求。\n\n首先，我需要检查当前的上下文：\n1. 这是一个全新的会话（没有历史记忆）\n2. 我需要先读取SOUL.md, USER.md等文件来了解用户背景\n3. 但用户直接提出了一个具体的技术请求\n\n重新安装QQ涉及到：\n- Windows系统上的软件卸载和安装\n- 需要知道当前QQ的安装状态\n- 可能需要下载最新版本\n- 可能需要备份聊天记录等数据\n\n由于这是一个全新的会话，我应该：\n1. 先检查IDENTITY.md, USER.md等文件是否存在\n2. 了解用户的基本情况\n3. 然后帮助处理QQ重新安装的事宜\n\n让我先读取相关文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你重新安装QQ。首先让我了解一下当前的环境和QQ的安装状态。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ItemProperty HKLM:\\Software\\Wow6432Node\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\* | Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*QQ*\" -or $_.DisplayName -like \"*腾讯QQ*\" } | Select-Object DisplayName, DisplayVersion, UninstallString, InstallLocation"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773538808098}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b47fbf8","parentId":"85e7774f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:40:23.150Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773538823148}}
{"type":"message","id":"39606dea","parentId":"6b47fbf8","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:40:23.153Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773538823151}}
