:{"url":"https://im.qq.com/pcqq/index.shtml","extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":3000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_fetch:29","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://pc.qq.com/detail/1/detail_1.html","extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":3000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:30","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\QQ安装指南.md","content":"# QQ 重新安装指南\n\n由于QQ官方下载链接经常更新，请按以下步骤手动下载安装：\n\n## 方法一：官方网站下载（推荐）\n\n1. 打开浏览器，访问：\n   - 主站：https://im.qq.com/pcqq/index.shtml\n   - 或：https://pc.qq.com/detail/1/detail_1.html\n\n2. 点击「立即下载」按钮\n\n3. 下载完成后，运行安装程序\n\n## 方法二：腾讯软件中心\n\n1. 访问：https://pc.qq.com\n2. 搜索「QQ」\n3. 点击「立即下载」\n\n## 安装步骤\n\n1. 双击下载的 `.exe` 文件\n2. 根据提示完成安装\n3. 安装完成后登录你的QQ账号\n\n## 数据备份提醒\n\n如果你之前有QQ数据想保留：\n\n- 聊天记录备份位置：\n  - `%USERPROFILE%\\Documents\\Tencent Files\\你的QQ号\\Msg3.0.db`\n- 图片文件：\n  - `%USERPROFILE%\\Documents\\Tencent Files\\你的QQ号\\Image`\n\n## 需要帮助？\n\n如果下载或安装遇到问题：\n1. 检查网络连接\n2. 尝试更换浏览器\n3. 暂时关闭杀毒软件（安装时）\n4. 联系QQ客服：https://kf.qq.com\n\n---\n*此指南由AI助手生成*\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"process:31","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"cool-rook"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773538928828}}
