{"type":"message","id":"ba0bc66c","parentId":"15e38612","timestamp":"2026-03-15T02:45:07.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问用户信息文件（IDENTITY.md、USER.md 等）存放在哪个目录下。根据系统提示，工作目录是 `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace`，所有用户相关的配置文件都存放在这里。\n\n我需要告诉用户这些文件的具体位置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你的用户信息文件都存放在以下目录：\n\n**📂 工作区路径：**\n```\nC:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\\n```\n\n**📝 具体文件位置：**\n\n| 文件 | 路径 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| IDENTITY.md | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md` | 我的身份信息（名字、性格等）|\n| USER.md | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md` | 你的用户信息 |\n| SOUL.md | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SOUL.md` | 我的核心行为准则 |\n| TOOLS.md | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md` | 本地工具配置 |\n| MEMORY.md | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md` | 长期记忆 |\n| memory/*.md | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\` | 每日记忆记录 |\n\n在 PowerShell 中可以用这个命令快速打开工作区：\n```powershell\nexplorer \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n```\n\n需要我帮你查看或修改哪个文件吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773542690909}}
